messages.messageBody:
I was born on Kinchelo (spelling?) Air Force Base in Kinross, MI. Good luck
in the UP! You will see a lot of snow, even in September and still in June in
a "good year". I don't really remember it there but have seen photos of our
little base house pretty much covered completely in a snow drift. Have fun!
And take up cross country skiing, gives you something to do in the winter.
Amanda
